name: I wish I was Cryptopunk
description: In NFT era, Cryptopunx took the reins of Internet. But I stayed unawared until I had to kick out some Cryptopunx out of my room. That was surrealistic! I don't know if it was real or just my imagination. But in any case, it made me think: I wish I was Cryptopunk too... But now it's too late.
